{"text_id":127831,"tokens":["Extra","curricular"," activities"," play"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," fostering"," the"," overall"," development"," of"," students"," and"," helping"," them"," cultivate"," various"," skills"," that"," cannot"," be"," solely"," acquired"," in"," a"," traditional"," classroom"," setting","."," By"," participating"," in"," extracurricular"," activities",","," students"," have"," the"," opportunity"," to"," engage"," in"," diverse"," interests",","," develop"," their"," talents",","," and"," build"," their"," capacity"," for"," collaboration",","," leadership",","," and"," time"," management","."," These"," activities"," also"," allow"," students"," to"," connect"," with"," like","-","minded"," individuals",","," fostering"," a"," sense"," of"," belonging"," and"," promoting"," social"," skills",".","\n\n","However",","," the"," debate"," surrounding"," whether"," extracurricular"," activities"," should"," be"," mandatory"," for"," all"," students"," is"," nuanced"," and"," deserves"," careful"," consideration","."," On"," the"," one"," hand",","," mand","ating"," such"," activities"," may"," ensure"," that"," all"," students"," have"," the"," opportunity"," to"," explore"," their"," interests"," and"," develop"," important"," skills","."," It"," can"," encourage"," students"," to"," step"," out"," of"," their"," comfort"," zones"," and"," try"," new"," things",","," ultimately"," enhancing"," their"," overall"," educational"," experience","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," some"," students"," may"," already"," have"," strenuous"," schedules"," due"," to"," academic"," or"," family"," commitments",","," making"," additional"," activities"," feel"," overwhelming"," or"," burdensome","."," ","\n\n","To"," address"," potential"," concerns",","," schools"," could"," implement"," flexible"," policies"," that"," take"," into"," account"," the"," diverse"," needs"," of"," students","."," For"," instance",","," schools"," could"," offer","